content:
I’m currently working as a postdoctoral researcher in the Department of Computer Science and Engineering at Seoul National University in South Korea.
My research topic lies in data privacy and security. Specifically, I’m interested in information flow control, trusted execution environment (TEE; Intel SGX, Arm TrustZone), privacy-preserving advertising, and so on.
